OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTikTok profits from        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flivestreams of refugees    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbegging                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Refugee families in Syrian camps are   
OL,6, begging for donations on TikTok while  
OL,7, the company takes up to 70% of the     
OL,8, proceeds, a BBC investigation found.   
OL,10,FChildren are livestreaming on the      
OL,11,Fsocial media app for hours, pleading   
OL,12,Ffor digital gifts with a cash value.   
OL,14,FThe BBC saw streams earning up to      
OL,15,F$1,000 (#900) an hour, but found       
OL,16,Frefugees received only a tiny fraction 
OL,17,Fof that.                               
OL,19,FTikTok said it would take prompt action
OL,20,Fagainst "exploitative begging".        
